Title: A Note on Conifolds
Authors: Kiyoshi Higashijima, Tetsuji Kimura and Muneto Nitta (Osaka Univ.)
Comments: LaTeX2e, 8 pages, no figures, accepted for publication in Physics
  Letters B
Report-no: OU-HET 390
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Mathematical Physics
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B518 (2001) 301-305
\\
  We present the Ricci-flat metric and its Kahler potential on the conifold
with the O(N) isometry, whose conical singularity is repaired by the complex
quadric surface Q^{N-2} = SO(N)/SO(N-2)xU(1).
